# Ownership por modulo

Antes de editar, confirmar modulo y archivos permitidos en Task Card o Feature Brief.

| Modulo | Rutas exclusivas | Vistas |
| --- | --- | --- |
| requisitions | `routes/modules/requisitions.php` | `resources/views/modules/requisitions/` |
| supplies | `routes/modules/supplies.php` | `resources/views/modules/suministros/` |
| quality-documents | `routes/modules/quality-documents.php` | `resources/views/modules/quality-documents/` |
| operaciones | `routes/areas/operaciones.php` | `resources/views/areas/operaciones/` |
| comercial | `routes/areas/comercial.php` | `resources/views/areas/comercial/` |
| admin-users | `routes/web.php` (grupo admin) | `resources/views/admin/` |

Tabla completa: [`docs/AGENT_WORKFLOW.md`](../../docs/AGENT_WORKFLOW.md)

No mezclar cambios de modulos distintos en una sola tarea sin AgentSj.
